al_system_is_in__awful_mess_/ |date=9 January 2014 |title=Worcester judge says legal system is in 'awful mess' |first=James |last=Connell |work=Worcester News}}</ref> ******* James Cadbury (b. 1985) a descendant of John Cadbury, setup up Love Cocoa in 2016, an organic, ethical, British chocolate company, which sends chocolate through the post in letterbox friendly boxes.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/06/30/cadbury-descendant-launches-chocolate-gift-delivery-brand-love-c/ |title=Cadbury descendant launches chocolate gift delivery brand Love Cocoa |work=The Telegraph |first=Lauren |last=Davidson |date=30 June 2016}}</ref>
